module JC_counter (
    input wire clk,
    input wire rst_n,
    output reg [63:0] Q
);

always @(posedge clk or negedge rst_n) begin
    if (!rst_n) begin
        Q <= 64'b0;
    end else begin
        if (Q[0] == 1'b0) begin
            Q <= {Q[62:0], 1'b1};
        end else begin
            Q <= {Q[62:0], 1'b0};
        end
    end
end

endmodule
